WEBVTT

00:00:09.804 --> 00:00:11.084
(Previously) Are you tired of me?

00:00:11.804 --> 00:00:13.203
For being such a troublemaker?

00:00:15.809 --> 00:00:17.073
I will never break up with you.

00:00:18.467 --> 00:00:19.467
Got it?

00:00:50.736 --> 00:00:52.771
Excuse me, I'm here to pick up an order.

00:00:53.371 --> 00:00:55.173
Sure, which one is it?

00:00:55.574 --> 00:00:56.574
This one.

00:00:57.442 --> 00:00:59.361
Oh, please wait a moment.

00:01:00.045 --> 00:01:01.045
Thank you.

00:01:01.296 --> 00:01:02.330
Here you go.

00:01:02.731 --> 00:01:03.418
Thank you.

00:01:03.418 --> 00:01:04.418
You're welcome.

00:01:08.887 --> 00:01:09.887
A gift in return.

00:01:10.489 --> 00:01:12.550
If someone gives you something, you should give back.

00:01:12.574 --> 00:01:14.214
In-In has given me so much over the years.

00:01:14.376 --> 00:01:15.961
This time, let's make it couple rings.

00:01:16.161 --> 00:01:17.446
The ultimate cute couple.

00:02:38.093 --> 00:02:38.894
Hello?

00:02:39.094 --> 00:02:40.094
Erng?

00:02:40.445 --> 00:02:41.763
Are you done buying shoes?

00:02:43.932 --> 00:02:45.132
I'm looking at them right now.

00:02:46.651 --> 00:02:48.336
Hmm, I haven't even looked at anything yet.

00:02:48.603 --> 00:02:51.006
Right now, I'm preparing to be your family's daughter-in-law.

00:02:53.775 --> 00:02:56.044
I ran into some friends, so we're having lunch.

00:02:56.761 --> 00:02:59.564
If you're done, come meet us at the restaurant on the corner.

00:03:00.332 --> 00:03:03.051
Hurry up. I miss you so much.

00:03:03.768 --> 00:03:04.768
Okay.

00:03:04.886 --> 00:03:06.254
Order some food for me too.

00:03:09.324 --> 00:03:10.442
No one will catch on.

00:03:10.926 --> 00:03:12.327
I'm being super smooth.

00:04:17.500 --> 00:04:25.400
"Chermchey" (Episode 9)

00:04:43.704 --> 00:04:46.689
This is P'O-ye, my boxing coach.

00:04:47.441 --> 00:04:50.465
And this is Yak, P'Ye's younger brother.

00:04:52.503 --> 00:04:55.363
And this is Erng Erng, my boyfriend.

00:04:56.097 --> 00:04:57.332
Hello.

00:05:00.030 --> 00:05:01.430
O-ye, ye, ye, yay!

00:05:01.455 --> 00:05:03.630
What kind of name is that?

00:05:03.990 --> 00:05:08.750
And Yak, wow, he's incredibly handsome.

00:05:10.128 --> 00:05:13.448
Your wife looks like he's in great shape, Maha.

00:05:13.515 --> 00:05:14.649
Your name is Erng, right?

00:05:15.417 --> 00:05:15.917
Yes.

00:05:16.165 --> 00:05:17.742
Interested in joining my boxing gym?

00:05:18.803 --> 00:05:19.803
Hey!

00:05:19.921 --> 00:05:21.122
I don't like violence.

00:05:21.656 --> 00:05:23.408
Even though I can kick down a banana tree.

00:05:23.725 --> 00:05:24.725
But no thanks.

00:05:25.493 --> 00:05:26.493
What are you laughing at?

00:05:26.761 --> 00:05:27.562
But seriously,

00:05:27.729 --> 00:05:28.930
I really don't like violence.

00:05:29.647 --> 00:05:30.448
Really?

00:05:30.648 --> 00:05:31.648
That's a shame.

00:05:32.167 --> 00:05:33.251
What about you, In?

00:05:33.768 --> 00:05:34.768
Are you interested?

00:05:35.403 --> 00:05:36.404
No thanks, Bro.

00:05:36.921 --> 00:05:38.373
My boyfriend and I run a bar.

00:05:39.057 --> 00:05:40.177
We don't have time to train.

00:05:42.727 --> 00:05:44.245
That's all for now.

00:05:44.729 --> 00:05:46.214
But make it medium spicy.

00:05:46.881 --> 00:05:48.650
Yak, I want it really spicy.

00:05:48.883 --> 00:05:50.123
I can't handle spicy food well.

00:05:50.251 --> 00:05:51.286
Then order your own dish.

00:05:51.453 --> 00:05:52.654
I'm afraid I won't finish it.

00:05:53.605 --> 00:05:55.657
They probably don't eat as spicy as you do.

00:05:59.574 --> 00:06:00.574
Fine.

00:06:04.532 --> 00:06:07.001
Why did you guys buy so much stuff?

00:06:07.285 --> 00:06:08.285
That's a ton of bags.

00:06:10.004 --> 00:06:12.123
Erng and I are going to the beach tomorrow.

00:06:13.291 --> 00:06:14.642
A relationship-building trip.

00:06:17.445 --> 00:06:19.964
How does going to the beach build a relationship?

00:06:22.083 --> 00:06:23.345
It actually works.

00:06:23.346 --> 00:06:26.171
Erng and I fell in love because of a trip we took.

00:06:30.291 --> 00:06:34.095
I'll bring back a cute daughter-in-law for you.

00:06:36.164 --> 00:06:37.482
But my name is Erng.

00:06:37.966 --> 00:06:39.167
I think I'm younger than you.

00:06:39.851 --> 00:06:40.885
I'm twenty-four.

00:06:41.603 --> 00:06:42.771
My name is Inta.

00:06:43.054 --> 00:06:44.406
You can just call me In.

00:06:46.007 --> 00:06:47.041
Or if you prefer,

00:06:48.610 --> 00:06:50.161
You can call me "darling"

00:06:55.049 --> 00:06:56.369
Do you know how to pray for love?

00:06:57.202 --> 00:06:58.202
Then follow me.

00:06:58.369 --> 00:06:59.404
I'll show you how.

00:06:59.854 --> 00:07:01.055
This is a piece of cake.

00:07:01.806 --> 00:07:03.641
Erng, do you have any plans after this?

00:07:04.976 --> 00:07:05.976
I don't know.

00:07:06.294 --> 00:07:07.654
I told you I don't have any plans.

00:07:09.247 --> 00:07:11.332
Erng, do you want shabu?

00:07:15.537 --> 00:07:16.654
That's my favorite!

00:07:21.443 --> 00:07:22.628
Let's go eat shabu.

00:07:23.537 --> 00:07:24.537
My treat.

00:07:25.697 --> 00:07:28.967
I won't say no because I'm starving right now.

00:07:35.373 --> 00:07:36.491
Here, take a look.

00:07:45.016 --> 00:07:46.016
Hmm?

00:07:50.088 --> 00:07:51.923
Where was your profile picture taken?

00:07:52.524 --> 00:07:53.524
Belgium.

00:07:54.893 --> 00:07:56.127
Is it really that great?

00:07:58.563 --> 00:07:59.563
You'll have to find out.

00:08:19.651 --> 00:08:21.085
If you have someone you like, Yak,

00:08:21.452 --> 00:08:22.687
Try asking them on a trip.

00:08:23.321 --> 00:08:24.801
You'll get to know each other better.

00:08:25.857 --> 00:08:27.125
I'll give it a try.

00:08:29.811 --> 00:08:31.095
Does that really work?

00:08:31.329 --> 00:08:32.769
You have to try it to find out, Bro.

00:08:35.333 --> 00:08:36.333
By the way,

00:08:37.157 --> 00:08:38.557
P'Ye, do you have a girlfriend yet?

00:08:45.727 --> 00:08:46.727
Not yet.

00:08:47.212 --> 00:08:49.092
I still want to enjoy my single life right now.

00:08:51.683 --> 00:08:52.683
Yak.

00:08:52.884 --> 00:08:54.052
Let me tag along.

00:08:54.852 --> 00:08:56.571
Why do you want to be a third wheel?

00:08:56.771 --> 00:08:57.771
Come on, little brother.

00:08:57.889 --> 00:08:59.329
Are you going to leave me all alone?

00:09:01.175 --> 00:09:02.443
Why don't you invite Ry?

00:09:03.094 --> 00:09:04.445
If you invite him,

00:09:04.562 --> 00:09:05.363
He'll definitely go.

00:09:05.563 --> 00:09:07.282
And how would you not be a third wheel?

00:09:08.566 --> 00:09:10.485
I might lose my virginity to Ry.

00:09:10.685 --> 00:09:11.685
But I think

00:09:11.769 --> 00:09:12.971
Ry probably won't go with you.

00:09:13.488 --> 00:09:15.173
You were too harsh on him the other day.

00:09:42.533 --> 00:09:43.533
Why?

00:09:44.464 --> 00:09:46.771
Why is everyone in love lately?

00:09:48.006 --> 00:09:49.123
If you're jealous,

00:09:50.174 --> 00:09:51.442
Then find a partner.

00:09:53.044 --> 00:09:54.529
That's a difficult task for me.

00:09:56.648 --> 00:09:58.333
Are you the one making it difficult?

00:09:59.167 --> 00:10:00.285
For my boyfriend and me,

00:10:01.336 --> 00:10:03.454
Love isn't hard at all.

00:10:06.174 --> 00:10:07.174
That's right.

00:10:08.326 --> 00:10:09.611
Inta and I,

00:10:10.695 --> 00:10:11.929
Nothing is difficult for us.

00:10:14.365 --> 00:10:16.651
It's not really that hard for me either.

00:10:17.201 --> 00:10:19.003
But lately at my gym,

00:10:19.253 --> 00:10:21.005
There's this guy hanging around.

00:10:21.806 --> 00:10:23.975
He acts like he owns me.

00:10:24.609 --> 00:10:26.010
It's so annoying, you know?

00:10:31.416 --> 00:10:33.735
The one named Cherry?

00:10:34.485 --> 00:10:35.887
Yeah, that's the one.

00:10:36.604 --> 00:10:39.805
But when he's not around, you get restless, don't you?

00:10:39.806 --> 00:10:42.326
Isn't that why you brought me to the mall to distract yourself?

00:10:42.777 --> 00:10:44.329
I don't feel guilty at all, okay?

00:10:45.647 --> 00:10:47.048
That's good then, Bro.

00:10:47.732 --> 00:10:49.367
You'll have time to find a partner.

00:10:52.854 --> 00:10:55.773
My boyfriend has plenty of cute friends.

00:10:57.575 --> 00:11:01.095
Erng, find a single one for my boss.

00:11:01.646 --> 00:11:02.646
Sure, I do.

00:11:04.042 --> 00:11:05.522
But what's your type, P'Ye?

00:11:05.935 --> 00:11:07.990
Do you like fair-skinned and cute,

00:11:08.293 --> 00:11:09.546
Or tan and sharp?

00:11:13.124 --> 00:11:14.139
Fair-skinned, I guess.

00:11:14.140 --> 00:11:15.140
And...

00:11:16.264 --> 00:11:17.264
High-pitched voice.

00:11:17.378 --> 00:11:18.378
High-pitched voice?

00:11:19.144 --> 00:11:20.144
High-pitched voice.

00:11:20.605 --> 00:11:26.378
Hello, In! It's Nok Nok. Interested in another girlfriend?

00:11:33.644 --> 00:11:35.413
What the hell are you guys sighing for?

00:11:38.366 --> 00:11:39.692
It's nothing, Bro.

00:11:40.243 --> 00:11:41.243
Erng,

00:11:41.531 --> 00:11:42.632
Introduce someone to P'Ye.

00:11:43.087 --> 00:11:45.456
Hey, no. I don't want anyone.

00:11:58.042 --> 00:12:01.498
(Ry: P'Ye, are you going to the beach? (With whom? And when?)

00:12:06.348 --> 00:12:09.214
(Ye: Nosy. You disappeared for days. (I thought my life was finally peaceful.)

00:12:09.215 --> 00:12:11.521
(Ry: Even if you're mean, I won't give up. (So, when are you going?)

00:12:11.545 --> 00:12:13.126
(Ye: I'm going on Saturday.)

00:12:20.142 --> 00:12:22.233
(Ry: Oh! I'm going to Samet this Saturday too. Can I hitch a ride?)

00:12:22.257 --> 00:12:23.452
(Ye: What about gas money?)

00:12:25.214 --> 00:12:27.714
(Ry: I'll give you my whole wallet and my heart.)

00:12:30.251 --> 00:12:31.251
What are you smiling at?

00:12:38.643 --> 00:12:40.611
What did you buy for the beach, Maha?

00:12:41.162 --> 00:12:42.362
I want to go to the beach too.

00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:44.165
I'm too lazy to make a list.

00:12:52.657 --> 00:12:53.657
Hey.

00:12:55.843 --> 00:12:56.843
Condoms, Bro.

00:12:57.161 --> 00:12:58.930
Shoot, why did I buy these?

00:12:59.497 --> 00:13:00.497
I'm going alone.

00:13:00.882 --> 00:13:01.882
Are you sure?

00:13:02.767 --> 00:13:04.647
Who were you smiling at on your phone just now?

00:13:05.770 --> 00:13:06.770
None of your business.

00:13:49.614 --> 00:13:50.614
Erng.

00:13:51.883 --> 00:13:52.883
We're here.

00:13:55.686 --> 00:13:56.721
Are we really here?

00:13:58.089 --> 00:13:59.089
Wow.

00:14:00.441 --> 00:14:03.169
The beach!

00:14:04.929 --> 00:14:05.929
Ah.

00:14:06.247 --> 00:14:07.365
The weather is so cool too.

00:14:23.965 --> 00:14:25.566
Wait in the car for a bit, sweetie.

00:14:26.417 --> 00:14:27.885
Mommy and Daddy will be right back.

00:14:29.287 --> 00:14:32.857
Why do you have to make me feel scared of such a cute doll?

00:14:34.208 --> 00:14:35.977
It's starting to look like a haunted doll.

00:14:37.161 --> 00:14:38.696
Watch the car for Daddy, okay?

00:14:39.730 --> 00:14:40.730
Come on.

00:14:42.250 --> 00:14:44.735
If Ern Ern answers back, I'm running.

00:14:59.450 --> 00:15:00.651
You're filming this too?

00:15:01.736 --> 00:15:03.337
To show our kids in the future

00:15:04.055 --> 00:15:05.655
That we once came to the beach together.

00:15:40.207 --> 00:15:41.207
Erng,

00:15:44.521 --> 00:15:46.213
Come be my model.

00:15:47.682 --> 00:15:48.682
Come on.

00:15:50.368 --> 00:15:51.368
Look handsome.

00:15:55.373 --> 00:15:56.373
One, two...

00:15:58.576 --> 00:15:59.576
Wow.

00:16:00.094 --> 00:16:01.094
That's amazing.

00:16:07.802 --> 00:16:09.202
It's not very crowded today, is it?

00:16:11.288 --> 00:16:12.690
That's how it is on weekdays.

00:16:13.724 --> 00:16:15.726
So, what made you want to bring me here?

00:16:18.129 --> 00:16:19.769
Well, I haven't been here in a long time.

00:16:21.732 --> 00:16:24.769
For me, the last time was during my junior year.

00:16:27.171 --> 00:16:28.171
As for me...

00:16:28.689 --> 00:16:29.689
High school.

00:16:30.091 --> 00:16:31.609
I lost my virginity right here.

00:16:32.610 --> 00:16:33.127
Huh?

00:16:33.128 --> 00:16:35.288
Is that really something you should be bragging about?

00:16:35.529 --> 00:16:36.529
Huh?

00:16:39.133 --> 00:16:40.260
What? Sex is a good thing, isn't it?

00:16:40.284 --> 00:16:41.452
Stop talking like that.

00:16:41.736 --> 00:16:42.970
Watch your mouth.

00:16:46.607 --> 00:16:47.725
Once we get there,

00:16:48.175 --> 00:16:49.935
Do you want to go swimming right away, Erng?

00:16:50.695 --> 00:16:51.695
Of course!

00:16:52.613 --> 00:16:54.765
I need to put on my mermaid tail for photos.

00:16:56.083 --> 00:16:57.968
Please be my photographer, Hia.

00:17:00.054 --> 00:17:01.255
What's my fee?

00:17:03.924 --> 00:17:05.009
You'll get something.

00:17:07.611 --> 00:17:08.771
You're so adorable, it hurts.

00:17:11.248 --> 00:17:12.883
That's just how cute people are.

00:18:11.375 --> 00:18:12.375
Which restaurant?

00:18:15.162 --> 00:18:17.565
This one. It has the best view on the island.

00:18:25.689 --> 00:18:26.724
Thanks, Hia.

00:19:20.411 --> 00:19:21.411
What's wrong?

00:19:21.645 --> 00:19:22.930
Why do you look so tense?

00:19:24.281 --> 00:19:25.281
I'm not tense.

00:19:26.217 --> 00:19:28.322
Yes, you are.

00:19:29.011 --> 00:19:32.103
Or did I pick a restaurant you don't like?

00:19:33.090 --> 00:19:34.090
I like it.

00:19:35.693 --> 00:19:37.127
Then why do you look so annoyed?

00:19:38.162 --> 00:19:39.162
I'm not annoyed.

00:19:39.366 --> 00:19:41.400
I just don't want that table staring at you.

00:19:42.733 --> 00:19:43.534
Are you jealous?

00:19:43.684 --> 00:19:44.858
Yes, I am.

00:19:44.859 --> 00:19:47.655
If you're going to look back, at least be subtle about it.

00:19:48.405 --> 00:19:50.925
And you even smiled at them.

00:19:52.126 --> 00:19:53.753
I smiled because I was laughing at you.

00:19:53.754 --> 00:19:55.129
I didn't smile at anyone else.

00:19:55.963 --> 00:19:56.963
Are you sure?

00:19:57.214 --> 00:19:58.214
Positive.

00:19:58.415 --> 00:20:00.017
I swear on my life.

00:20:00.601 --> 00:20:02.887
Did you ask the Buddha if he wanted you to swear on him?

00:20:03.137 --> 00:20:04.137
Gross.

00:20:04.722 --> 00:20:05.722
Oh, please.

00:20:05.890 --> 00:20:07.892
You didn't seem to mind when we were kissing.

00:20:14.882 --> 00:20:16.122
I'm not talking to you anymore.

00:20:18.135 --> 00:20:20.487
I didn't know Erng Erng could be this possessive.

00:20:21.255 --> 00:20:22.255
I am.

00:20:22.456 --> 00:20:23.456
Very possessive.

00:20:24.008 --> 00:20:25.209
I'm incredibly jealous.

00:20:26.443 --> 00:20:27.443
Aw.

00:20:28.012 --> 00:20:29.847
I thought I didn't matter to you.

00:20:32.049 --> 00:20:33.049
Of course you do.

00:20:34.134 --> 00:20:35.452
You're my sweetheart.

00:20:37.454 --> 00:20:38.522
Whose sweetheart?

00:20:39.123 --> 00:20:41.008
Erng Erng's one and only sweetheart.

00:20:46.267 --> 00:20:48.541
My heart doesn't belong to me anymore.

00:20:50.358 --> 00:20:52.577
I've given it all to Erng Erng.

00:20:58.976 --> 00:21:00.010
Excuse me.

00:21:00.611 --> 00:21:02.994
My friend really likes you.

00:21:02.995 --> 00:21:04.481
The way you smiled at her just now...

00:21:08.135 --> 00:21:09.370
Can she have your Line ID?

00:21:20.097 --> 00:21:22.967
Actually, I have a partner.

00:21:25.653 --> 00:21:26.826
That's okay.

00:21:26.827 --> 00:21:28.806
It's not like she's here with you.

00:21:30.774 --> 00:21:32.176
How do you know she's not here?

00:21:32.643 --> 00:21:33.444
Huh?

00:21:33.527 --> 00:21:34.611
Excuse me, girls.

00:21:35.496 --> 00:21:36.496
This guy right here...

00:21:36.780 --> 00:21:38.344
Is my boyfriend.

00:21:43.337 --> 00:21:44.605
Erng Erng, you're so direct.

00:21:46.256 --> 00:21:47.524
Stop laughing. What's so funny?

00:21:51.645 --> 00:21:55.364
Plus one point for Erng Erng's possessiveness.

00:21:55.970 --> 00:21:56.970
You're catching up to me.

00:21:59.086 --> 00:22:01.805
Sorry, we couldn't tell.

00:22:05.175 --> 00:22:06.175
Sure.

00:22:09.754 --> 00:22:11.433
See that? Huh?

00:22:12.333 --> 00:22:13.417
Stop laughing, Hia.

00:22:14.852 --> 00:22:16.053
You're just so adorable.

00:22:19.256 --> 00:22:20.656
Do you want to order anything else?

00:22:22.242 --> 00:22:23.494
Just the usual.

00:22:25.646 --> 00:22:26.646
Okay.

00:22:27.848 --> 00:22:29.333
I'll order for you.

00:22:32.369 --> 00:22:33.454
It's not funny at all.

00:22:35.205 --> 00:22:37.091
Some girl trying to steal my man.

00:22:40.894 --> 00:22:43.163
If they were even a fraction as dorky as you,

00:22:43.530 --> 00:22:45.080
Maybe I'd let them.

00:22:47.801 --> 00:22:50.401
Just because I love you, you think you can say whatever you want?

00:22:50.771 --> 00:22:51.771
Huh?

00:22:52.005 --> 00:22:53.005
No.

00:22:54.041 --> 00:22:55.041
I won't say it again.

00:22:55.609 --> 00:22:56.609
Too late.

00:22:57.127 --> 00:22:58.695
You're sleeping on the balcony tonight.

00:22:59.563 --> 00:23:00.364
No way.

00:23:00.531 --> 00:23:01.932
Then sleep on the floor.

00:23:02.483 --> 00:23:03.483
No to that, too.

00:23:06.349 --> 00:23:08.721
I want to sleep with Erng Erng.

00:23:09.807 --> 00:23:11.008
Go wherever you want.

00:23:15.045 --> 00:23:16.045
Hey!

00:23:16.130 --> 00:23:17.130
Erng!

00:23:22.736 --> 00:23:23.736
Come here.

00:23:24.455 --> 00:23:25.455
Get up.

00:23:25.856 --> 00:23:27.324
We're leaving. Grab your bag.

00:23:28.571 --> 00:23:29.680
Let go of me first.

00:23:31.680 --> 00:23:32.839
Hurry up.

00:23:32.840 --> 00:23:33.840
Still laughing?

00:23:35.532 --> 00:23:37.134
Stop looking at that table.

00:23:38.168 --> 00:23:39.229
Why are you staring so much?

00:23:39.253 --> 00:23:40.253
Let's go.

00:23:41.205 --> 00:23:42.205
Hurry.

00:23:51.532 --> 00:23:53.817
Hia, let me see the photos.

00:23:59.606 --> 00:24:00.606
Here.

00:24:06.763 --> 00:24:07.763
Wow.

00:24:08.415 --> 00:24:09.975
You're a really good photographer, Hia.

00:24:10.968 --> 00:24:13.288
If I didn't take good ones, I'd have to hear you complain.

00:24:14.004 --> 00:24:15.572
Am I really that much of a whiner?

00:24:16.323 --> 00:24:17.323
Yes.

00:24:17.374 --> 00:24:18.374
You complain a lot.

00:24:19.610 --> 00:24:21.953
In the morning, I wake you up and you complain you're tired.

00:24:21.954 --> 00:24:23.323
At noon, you complain you're hungry.

00:24:23.324 --> 00:24:24.839
When we take photos, you complain it's too hot.

00:24:24.840 --> 00:24:27.367
When you eat a bit too much, you complain you're full.

00:24:28.042 --> 00:24:30.971
And tonight, you'll complain you can't sleep.

00:24:31.205 --> 00:24:32.806
Are you holding something back?

00:24:34.441 --> 00:24:35.441
No.

00:24:36.326 --> 00:24:38.366
Relax, I’m just explaining so you get the picture.

00:24:40.097 --> 00:24:41.862
Fine.

00:24:42.137 --> 00:24:43.925
I'll try to complain less.

00:24:46.403 --> 00:24:47.403
No need.

00:24:48.963 --> 00:24:50.780
I like listening to it. It's funny.

00:24:53.177 --> 00:24:54.177
Psycho.

00:24:55.445 --> 00:24:58.649
Lucky you, having a psycho for a husband.

00:25:01.134 --> 00:25:03.494
Are you suffering from heatstroke? You're talking nonsense.

00:25:04.404 --> 00:25:05.528
I don't have heatstroke.

00:25:06.574 --> 00:25:08.037
I'm just seasick.

00:25:10.811 --> 00:25:12.963
And when exactly did you go out to sea?

00:25:13.647 --> 00:25:14.448
Huh?

00:25:14.565 --> 00:25:16.683
Didn't you feel the waves on the boat ride over?

00:25:19.203 --> 00:25:20.203
Hey.

00:25:21.121 --> 00:25:22.372
The sun is starting to go down.

00:25:22.656 --> 00:25:23.896
Do you want to go in the water?

00:25:25.976 --> 00:25:26.976
Sure.

00:26:38.215 --> 00:26:39.766
Hia! Oh no, I'm drowning!

00:26:49.693 --> 00:26:50.693
Wait, what are you doing?

00:26:50.894 --> 00:26:51.894
Giving you CPR.

00:26:52.529 --> 00:26:53.614
Weren't you drowning?

00:26:53.930 --> 00:26:56.216
I wasn't drowning. I was just playing.

00:26:56.967 --> 00:26:58.407
I thought you wanted mouth-to-mouth.

00:27:00.654 --> 00:27:01.654
I don't.

00:27:02.656 --> 00:27:04.207
But can I get a piggyback ride?

00:27:08.328 --> 00:27:09.328
Sure.

00:27:09.730 --> 00:27:10.730
Jump on.

00:27:12.566 --> 00:27:14.451
Are you sure you can carry me?

00:27:14.935 --> 00:27:15.736
Yeah.

00:27:15.852 --> 00:27:17.287
I can carry my own wife.

00:27:18.605 --> 00:27:19.605
Okay.

00:27:26.697 --> 00:27:28.882
Giddy up, my white stallion!

00:27:41.411 --> 00:27:42.496
Hey, we're going to sink!

00:29:00.574 --> 00:29:01.574
Hia.

00:29:02.178 --> 00:29:06.605
Can I do something really sexy and bold just once in my life, Hia?

00:29:09.816 --> 00:29:11.051
Like what, beautiful?

00:29:14.054 --> 00:29:16.656
I'm honestly amazed by Erng Erng's confidence.

00:29:17.891 --> 00:29:18.891
So beautiful.

00:29:20.494 --> 00:29:21.494
So sexy.

00:29:22.529 --> 00:29:23.529
Thank you.

00:29:24.448 --> 00:29:25.816
But I don't support this.

00:29:27.417 --> 00:29:29.252
My Erng Erng should be the sweet type.

00:29:29.603 --> 00:29:31.888
That would match the pastel beads I bought you.

00:29:33.056 --> 00:29:34.056
Oh, please.

00:29:34.975 --> 00:29:36.176
Open your eyes and look.

00:29:37.244 --> 00:29:38.895
I'm dripping with sweetness.

00:29:40.697 --> 00:29:42.215
You don't sound very convinced, Hia.

00:29:42.732 --> 00:29:44.768
I told you, I want you to be the sweet type.

00:29:45.936 --> 00:29:47.424
Who acts sweet at the beach?

00:29:47.562 --> 00:29:49.357
You have to look hot and sexy.

00:29:49.358 --> 00:29:51.029
Wear a bikini and make it hot.

00:29:51.408 --> 00:29:53.577
Thailand's sun is already hot enough.

00:29:56.930 --> 00:29:57.930
Come on.

00:29:58.042 --> 00:30:00.798
Can't I be hot and sexy for just one day, Hia?

00:30:02.135 --> 00:30:03.403
Fine.

00:30:06.573 --> 00:30:09.776
But don't do splits in that mermaid tail. It'll rip.

00:30:10.694 --> 00:30:11.694
Oh, gosh.

00:30:11.812 --> 00:30:15.615
I want a cute pose, like Princess Ariel.

00:30:16.049 --> 00:30:17.577
Ariel is iconic.

00:30:17.578 --> 00:30:20.136
She came ashore to snag a man. Have you seen it?

00:30:21.521 --> 00:30:22.521
Of course.

00:30:23.573 --> 00:30:26.610
But I felt bad for her, having to trade her voice for legs.

00:30:27.894 --> 00:30:30.931
How sweet of you to feel bad for Ariel.

00:30:33.650 --> 00:30:35.287
Give me a set of Ariel poses, then.

00:30:35.755 --> 00:30:37.005
To show your sympathy for her.

00:30:37.921 --> 00:30:38.921
Wow.

00:30:39.732 --> 00:30:40.732
You got it.

00:31:08.168 --> 00:31:09.336
Absolutely perfect.

00:31:10.654 --> 00:31:11.654
Hia.

00:31:12.340 --> 00:31:14.006
Should we watch the sunset?

00:31:15.242 --> 00:31:17.527
Yeah, I was just about to suggest that.

00:31:20.447 --> 00:31:21.447
Hia.

00:31:22.566 --> 00:31:23.566
Actually,

00:31:24.651 --> 00:31:26.336
I have something to give you, Hia.

00:31:29.573 --> 00:31:31.691
You've given me so many things already.

00:31:32.442 --> 00:31:34.761
It's time I give you something in return.

00:32:00.654 --> 00:32:01.688
This ring is for you,

00:32:02.372 --> 00:32:03.373
And this one is for me.

00:32:04.924 --> 00:32:06.244
Let's wear them as a couple, Hia.

00:32:07.377 --> 00:32:09.296
So everyone knows you're taken.

00:32:10.530 --> 00:32:11.850
Because I've already claimed you.

00:32:15.135 --> 00:32:16.135
Uh...

00:32:18.455 --> 00:32:19.455
What's with the "uh"?

00:32:19.995 --> 00:32:21.491
Are you not going to accept my ring?

00:32:23.610 --> 00:32:24.610
No, it's not that.

00:32:25.616 --> 00:32:26.616
It's just...

00:32:28.289 --> 00:32:29.801
I bought a couple's ring set too.

00:32:32.912 --> 00:32:33.912
No way!

00:32:44.297 --> 00:32:45.297
Really.

00:32:46.850 --> 00:32:48.284
We're totally on the same page.

00:33:11.124 --> 00:33:12.442
Actually, it's pretty great.

00:33:14.928 --> 00:33:16.728
It shows we were both thinking of each other.

00:33:19.883 --> 00:33:21.055
So...

00:33:22.349 --> 00:33:25.047
What do we do now? Which ones should we wear?

00:33:27.006 --> 00:33:28.398
Just wear both of them.

00:33:29.279 --> 00:33:30.279
That'd look so cool.

00:33:31.211 --> 00:33:32.255
Yeah, you're right.

00:33:32.998 --> 00:33:33.998
Let's do this.

00:33:35.067 --> 00:33:36.324
We'll put them on each other.

00:33:39.252 --> 00:33:40.252
Okay.

00:35:50.366 --> 00:35:52.001
We're going to set this place on fire!

00:35:55.054 --> 00:35:56.054
How so?

00:36:09.569 --> 00:36:13.523
Let them see how fabulous the owner of a Chermchey can be.

00:36:36.420 --> 00:36:38.047
Hia, get up and dance with me.

00:36:38.364 --> 00:36:39.532
No way, I'm embarrassed.

00:36:39.883 --> 00:36:42.168
Oh, come on. You're still shy at this point?

00:36:42.769 --> 00:36:43.269
Yeah.

00:36:43.682 --> 00:36:44.682
Come on.

00:37:23.443 --> 00:37:26.012
Show them what the owner of a Chermchey is made of!

00:37:28.364 --> 00:37:29.364
Erng.

00:37:30.166 --> 00:37:31.417
Tonight is our last night.

00:37:34.003 --> 00:37:35.003
Let's...

00:37:39.609 --> 00:37:41.849
Let's do Maruko. (Short for "Yeye Maruko," to fuck)

00:37:47.216 --> 00:37:48.451
You like her too?

00:37:50.803 --> 00:37:51.803
Yeah.

00:38:03.483 --> 00:38:04.968
Are we talking about the same Maruko?

00:38:06.336 --> 00:38:09.122
The one with short hair?

00:38:09.656 --> 00:38:13.126
Oh my god, do you understand anything at all?

00:38:14.327 --> 00:38:16.295
Man, you're hopeless tonight, Hia.

00:38:16.929 --> 00:38:17.929
Hey!

00:38:18.815 --> 00:38:19.815
Whoa!

00:38:20.083 --> 00:38:21.083
Erng.

00:38:24.003 --> 00:38:25.003
Erng.

00:38:26.684 --> 00:38:27.774
It's not finished yet.

00:38:28.574 --> 00:38:29.574
That's enough.

00:38:34.697 --> 00:38:35.848
We were doing Maruko!

00:38:37.850 --> 00:38:39.369
The one with short hair?

00:38:39.535 --> 00:38:40.535
Yeah, come here.

00:38:45.491 --> 00:38:48.094
Hey, you haven't paid yet, kid!

00:38:52.248 --> 00:38:53.248
Oh, man.

00:38:55.735 --> 00:38:57.086
Fine, I'll pay.

00:38:59.122 --> 00:39:00.122
Why like this everytime

00:40:24.939 --> 00:40:26.400
Intha &amp; Akara

00:40:27.299 --> 00:40:30.939
I used to think love had to be difficult,

00:40:31.882 --> 00:40:32.882
Exhausting,

00:40:33.709 --> 00:40:35.330
And painful before you could have it.

00:40:36.813 --> 00:40:38.563
But since I've been with Hia In...

00:40:38.564 --> 00:40:40.564
I feel like...

00:40:41.148 --> 00:40:42.923
Love is actually very simple.

00:40:43.597 --> 00:40:45.143
It's just about two people

00:40:45.772 --> 00:40:47.772
Who simply want to have each other by their side.

00:40:48.806 --> 00:40:51.099
After all the chaos passed,

00:40:52.312 --> 00:40:54.269
I just wanted to see Erng smile more.

00:40:54.898 --> 00:40:57.179
So I tried doing silly things to make him laugh every day.

00:40:57.667 --> 00:40:59.218
Who would have thought

00:40:59.442 --> 00:41:01.891
That Hia In would actually buy me a mermaid tail?

00:41:02.993 --> 00:41:05.383
I only said it as a joke,

00:41:05.967 --> 00:41:07.967
But he actually remembered.

00:41:08.866 --> 00:41:10.347
Erng always acts shy,

00:41:11.021 --> 00:41:13.021
But when he gets something he really likes,

00:41:13.381 --> 00:41:14.673
His eyes sparkle.

00:41:15.572 --> 00:41:16.814
Just like a kid with a new toy.

00:41:18.027 --> 00:41:19.648
Some nights, I wonder...

00:41:20.322 --> 00:41:22.638
If Erng hadn't followed me that day,

00:41:23.672 --> 00:41:25.672
What would my life be like right now?

00:41:26.481 --> 00:41:27.724
I might still be lonely,

00:41:29.162 --> 00:41:31.466
Still talking trash to everyone,

00:41:32.814 --> 00:41:34.814
And having no one to nag me like this.

00:41:35.314 --> 00:41:37.431
I used to be so afraid of commitment.

00:41:39.010 --> 00:41:40.421
But now,

00:41:40.921 --> 00:41:42.769
I'm only afraid of one thing.

00:41:43.173 --> 00:41:45.173
I'm afraid of the day I won't have Hia by my side.

00:41:46.141 --> 00:41:48.006
When Erng disappeared for a while,

00:41:48.815 --> 00:41:51.095
I thought he sneaked off to buy snacks again.

00:41:52.174 --> 00:41:55.440
I never expected him to prepare something like that for me.

00:41:55.889 --> 00:41:56.990
And the world...

00:41:57.619 --> 00:42:00.698
Always seems to throw strange people into my life.

00:42:01.318 --> 00:42:02.948
Like a fierce-looking teacher,

00:42:03.712 --> 00:42:04.952
And a handsome younger brother.

00:42:05.515 --> 00:42:09.190
But honestly, when we're all together, it's hilarious.

00:42:10.000 --> 00:42:11.803
I think the most stubborn person

00:42:13.060 --> 00:42:15.244
Is usually the one who falls in love the easiest.

00:42:15.693 --> 00:42:17.015
I love the sea.

00:42:17.779 --> 00:42:19.546
It feels like the whole world goes quiet,

00:42:20.000 --> 00:42:23.639
Leaving only the sound of the waves and the voice of the one I love.

00:42:24.583 --> 00:42:26.718
I love taking photos with Hia.

00:42:27.951 --> 00:42:29.640
Because in every photo he takes,

00:42:30.312 --> 00:42:33.411
It feels like he truly sees me as the cutest person in the world.

00:42:33.991 --> 00:42:35.605
I was laughing so hard back then.

00:42:36.593 --> 00:42:39.073
Erng was being so openly jealous,

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:41.932
But it was incredibly cute.

00:42:41.933 --> 00:42:43.872
Yes, I'm jealous.

00:42:44.456 --> 00:42:45.472
So what?

00:42:46.147 --> 00:42:47.858
This guy is my boyfriend!

00:42:48.442 --> 00:42:50.577
Every time Erng says I'm important to him,

00:42:51.296 --> 00:42:52.981
I still get just as shy.

00:42:53.610 --> 00:42:55.362
I don't know why.

00:42:55.632 --> 00:42:58.834
I intended to be hot and set the beach on fire.

00:42:59.373 --> 00:43:00.429
But in the end,

00:43:01.283 --> 00:43:04.137
Hia teased me into being a sweet Ariel again.

00:43:04.991 --> 00:43:06.067
Erng doesn't realize

00:43:07.235 --> 00:43:09.037
That even when he sulks or grumbles all day,

00:43:10.206 --> 00:43:11.380
He's still adorable.

00:43:12.144 --> 00:43:14.033
Sometimes happiness is simple.

00:43:14.977 --> 00:43:16.170
Just playing in the water,

00:43:16.889 --> 00:43:18.175
Laughing,

00:43:18.399 --> 00:43:20.000
And teasing each other.

00:43:20.261 --> 00:43:21.740
That's more than enough.

00:43:22.240 --> 00:43:25.032
I don't know what the future holds,

00:43:26.149 --> 00:43:28.087
But right now, I only know one thing.

00:43:30.087 --> 00:43:32.086
I want every trip from now on

00:43:32.087 --> 00:43:33.646
To have Erng by my side.

00:43:34.230 --> 00:43:37.982
Honestly, I was so nervous when I gave him the ring.

00:43:38.746 --> 00:43:40.456
My heart was beating like crazy.

00:43:41.580 --> 00:43:43.271
It felt like I was proposing or something.

00:43:44.170 --> 00:43:45.480
And it was such a coincidence,

00:43:46.918 --> 00:43:48.317
Because I bought a ring too.

00:43:49.692 --> 00:43:51.292
Maybe when people truly love each other,

00:43:52.313 --> 00:43:55.013
They think of the same things at the same time.

00:43:56.631 --> 00:44:00.661
In the end, no matter how beautiful the sea is,

00:44:01.021 --> 00:44:03.376
What makes this trip the most special

00:44:03.915 --> 00:44:06.157
Is having Hia here with me.

00:44:06.786 --> 00:44:09.146
If you ask what our love is like,

00:44:11.033 --> 00:44:12.543
It's probably just like this.

00:44:12.768 --> 00:44:14.917
Chaotic, playful,

00:44:15.232 --> 00:44:16.672
And sulking with each other all day.

00:44:17.507 --> 00:44:20.000
But in the end, we still choose each other.

00:44:24.596 --> 00:44:26.676
(Next episode) Being with you makes me feel so small.

00:44:28.214 --> 00:44:29.530
Isn't that a good thing?

00:44:31.686 --> 00:44:32.605
Erng.

00:44:32.606 --> 00:44:37.391
When we grow old, can we be Uncle In and Aunt Erng here together?

00:44:38.987 --> 00:44:40.982
When I said I wanted to marry you,

00:44:42.510 --> 00:44:43.687
I wasn't joking.

